      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's... unusual. The blueprints specify a tight tolerance for this load-bearing section. If you're saying the slab is 2 inches larger on all sides, that changes the entire footprint of the structural framing. Can you double-check your sensors? I need to be sure there wasn't a calibration error before I sign off on this.",
